# Multi-Tenant Platform: System Architecture

---

## 1. Database Architecture (ERD)

**Dual-Database Strategy:**
- **Master DB (`mysql`)** → Platform-wide metadata: tenants, billing, modules.
- **Tenant DB (`tenant_dynamic`)** → Isolated per-tenant data: users, products, orders.

```mermaid
erDiagram
    TENANT ||--o{ TENANT_DOMAIN : hosts
    TENANT ||--o{ TENANT_MODULE : subscribes
    TENANT ||--o{ INVOICE : billed
    TENANT ||--o| TENANT_DATABASE_PLAN : uses
    TENANT ||--o{ TENANT_DATABASE_STAT : snapshots
    TENANT ||--o{ PAYMENT_METHOD : stores
    TENANT ||--o{ PAYMENT : makes
    TENANT ||--o{ DOMAIN_ORDER : orders
    MODULE ||--o{ TENANT_MODULE : active_in

    TENANT {
        bigint id PK
        string tenant_id UK "Slug e.g. acme"
        string database_name "tenant_acme"
        string db_username "tu_acme (isolated)"
        string db_password_encrypted "AES-256"
        enum status "active/suspended/billing_failed/terminated"
        enum provisioning_status "pending/db_created/migrated/active/failed"
        int database_plan_id FK
    }
    MODULE {
        int id PK
        string module_key "ecommerce, crm"
        string module_name
        decimal price
        boolean is_active
    }
    INVOICE {
        int id PK
        string tenant_id FK
        decimal amount
        enum status "pending/paid/overdue"
    }
    TENANT_DATABASE_PLAN {
        int id PK
        string slug "starter/business"
        int storage_limit_mb
        int max_tables
        int max_connections
    }
```

---

## 2. Complete Feature Map

### 🌍 Models (Master DB)

| Model | Connection | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| [Tenant](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Tenant.php#8-121) | `mysql` | Slug ID, encrypted DB creds, provisioning state machine (`pending→active`), status control (`active/suspended/terminated`). Relations: domains, modules, invoices, payments, stats, plan. |
| `TenantDomain` | `mysql` | Subdomain/custom domain records. Fields: `is_primary`, `is_verified`, `status`. |
| [TenantModule](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantModule.php#7-71) | `mysql` | Junction table for subscriptions. Fields: `status`, `expires_at`, `auto_renew`, `price_paid`. Scopes: [active()](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Module.php#33-40). |
| [TenantDatabasePlan](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantDatabasePlan.php#8-56) | `mysql` | Storage plans. Fields: `storage_limit_mb`, `max_tables`, `max_connections`, `price`. Scopes: [active()](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Module.php#33-40). |
| [TenantDatabaseStat](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantDatabaseStat.php#8-67) | `mysql` | Time-series snapshots of tenant DB size. Fields: `database_size_mb`, `slow_query_count`, `write_operation_count`, `top_tables_by_growth` (JSON). |
| [Module](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Module.php#7-49) | `mysql` | Platform-wide feature definitions. Relations: [tenantModules](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Tenant.php#113-120), [activeSubscriptions](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Module.php#33-40). |
| [Invoice](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Invoice.php#8-147) | `mysql` | Billing records per tenant. Fields: `status`, `due_date`, `paid_at`. |
| [Payment](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/Payment.php#7-85) | `mysql` | Stripe payment records. Fields: `stripe_session_id`, `stripe_payment_intent_id`, `amount_paid`, `status`. |
| [PaymentMethod](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/PaymentMethod.php#8-128) | `mysql` | Saved cards per tenant. Fields: `stripe_payment_method_id`, `brand`, `last_four`, `is_default`. |
| `DomainOrder` | `mysql` | Namecheap domain purchase records. Fields: `domain_name`, `years`, `expires_at`, `status`. |
| [SuperAdmin](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/SuperAdmin.php#10-61) | `mysql` | Platform admin accounts. Uses Sanctum for authentication. |

### 🧩 Models (Tenant DB)

| Model | Connection | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| [User](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/User.php#11-52) | `tenant_dynamic` | Per-tenant users. Fields: `role (admin/manager/user)`, `status`. Uses Sanctum. |
| [TenantBaseModel](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantBaseModel.php#12-30) | `tenant_dynamic` | Abstract base model. Hard-codes `tenant_dynamic` connection for all tenant models to prevent accidental cross-DB queries. |
| `Ecommerce\Product`, [Order](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/Api/DomainStoreController.php#522-572), `Customer`, etc. | `tenant_dynamic` | All extend [TenantBaseModel](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantBaseModel.php#12-30). Scoped to the current tenant's isolated database automatically. |

