### 🛡️ Middlewares (`app/Http/Middleware`)

| Middleware | Alias | Applied On | Features |
|---|---|---|---|
| [IdentifyTenant](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Http/Middleware/IdentifyTenant.php#13-141) | _(class ref)_ | All tenant routes | Resolves tenant from `X-Tenant-ID` header → custom domain lookup → subdomain extraction. Switches `tenant_dynamic` DB. Blocks `suspended/terminated/billing_failed` tenants. |
| `AuthenticateToken` | _(class ref)_ | Protected tenant routes | Validates custom HS256 JWT. Decodes user ID and tenant ID from token. Attaches `user_id` to request. |
| [CheckModuleAccess](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Http/Middleware/CheckModuleAccess.php#10-45) | `module.access` | Ecommerce routes (`module.access:ecommerce`) | Checks [TenantModule](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantModule.php#7-71) subscription record. Returns `402 Payment Required` if inactive. |
| [EnforceDatabaseQuota](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Http/Middleware/EnforceDatabaseQuota.php#10-75) | `quota.enforce` | Write routes (POST/PUT/PATCH) | Checks latest [TenantDatabaseStat](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantDatabaseStat.php#8-67) against [TenantDatabasePlan](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Models/TenantDatabasePlan.php#8-56). Blocks if storage **or** table limit exceeded. |
| `DynamicCors` | _(auto)_ | All routes | Dynamically sets CORS `Allow-Origin` based on verified tenant domains. Prevents cross-tenant cookie/session attacks. |

