### ⚙️ Services (`app/Services`)

| Service | Features |
|---|---|
| [DatabaseManager](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#9-217) | [createTenantDatabase](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#18-50), [runTenantMigrations](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#51-99) (raw SQL: `users` + `personal_access_tokens`), [createAdminUser](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#80-106), [switchToTenantDatabase](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#171-216) (purges & reconnects `tenant_dynamic`), [getTenantConnection](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#107-143) (connection cache). |
